verses.verse: A <S%H7892>Song<s%> of <S%H4609>degrees<s%>. <S%H835>Blessed<s%> is every one that <S%H3373>feareth<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%>; that <S%H1980>walketh<s%> in his <S%H1870>ways<s%>.
For thou shalt <S%H398>eat<s%> the <S%H3018>labour<s%> of thine <S%H3709>hands<s%>: <S%H835>happy<s%> shalt thou be, and it shall be <S%H2896>well<s%> with thee.

Thy <S%H802>wife<s%> shall be as a <S%H6509>fruitful<s%> <S%H1612>vine<s%> by the <S%H3411>sides<s%> of thine <S%H1004>house<s%>: thy <S%H1121>children<s%> like <S%H2132>olive<s%> <S%H8363>plants<s%> round <S%H5439>about<s%> thy <S%H7979>table<s%>.
Behold, that thus shall the <S%H1397>man<s%> be <S%H1288>blessed<s%> that <S%H3373>feareth<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%>.

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> shall <S%H1288>bless<s%> thee out of <S%H6726>Zion<s%>: and thou shalt <S%H7200>see<s%> the <S%H2898>good<s%> of <S%H3389>Jerusalem<s%> all the <S%H3117>days<s%> of thy <S%H2416>life<s%>.
Yea, thou shalt <S%H7200>see<s%> thy <S%H1121>children's<s%> <S%H1121>children<s%>, and <S%H7965>peace<s%> upon <S%H3478>Israel<s%>.
